00:43:04.840 --> 00:43:06.260
But I'm sorry that
that happened to you.

00:43:06.260 --> 00:43:07.470
That's really sad for me.

00:43:07.470 --> 00:43:08.590
I'm serious.

00:43:08.590 --> 00:43:10.710
I hate it when
people tell me that.

